Get Skills working with Real Businesses In Yafip Internship Program.

Giving young persons the opportunity to be trained, become self employed, reduce unemployment and develop their businesses, pursue their dreams and contribute productively to the growth of the economy.

What is Yafip?

Youth Alive Fellowship Internship Programme (YAFIP) is a training platform put together under the umbrella of the Living Faith Church Youth Alive Fellowship. The programme, which started since 2018.

  • Offers youths the opportunity to gain practical on-the-job training.
  • Experience in different fields of choice.
  • Providing the opportunity of working directly with inspiring and experienced professionals.
  • Acquiring the necessary business management and marketing skills required to run a business.

Eligibilty Criteria

Be a lover of God

Candidate applying for this internship should be a lover of God and his word.

Passion

Must have passion for the chosen vocation.

Ability to Read

Ability to read and write in English language.

Computer

Computer literacy may be an added advantage.

Testimonial

Pelumi Akinlabi

Being a part of YAFIP has made me to fulfill my dream. I have been thinking of how to become a photographer but didn't get the opportunity to because I lacked the necessary funds and so couldn't learn . To my greatest surprise I got to know about YAFIP and realized the internship program was free so I took advantage of it. Now I can handle camera as a real professional without being scared
